<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Asparsh — Student web developer portfolio showcasing projects, services, and contact information.">
    <link rel="icon" href="assets/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="show.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&family=Montserrat:wght@500;700&family=Raleway:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Asparsh | Student Portfolio">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Student web developer portfolio showcasing projects, services, and contact information.">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:image" content="assets/biography-image.jpg">
    <title>Asparsh | Portfolio</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="user-logo">
            <a href="#home"><p>Asparsh</p></a>
        </div>
        <input type="checkbox" id="nav-toggle" class="nav-toggle" aria-hidden="true">
        <nav>
            <label for="nav-toggle" class="menu-toggle" aria-label="Toggle navigation menu">
                <span class="bar"></span>
                <span class="bar"></span>
                <span class="bar"></span>
            </label>
            <ul id="primary-nav" class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
                <li><a href="#blog">Blog</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact" class="contact-link">Contact Me</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <label for="nav-toggle" class="nav-overlay" id="nav-overlay" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true"></label>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="home" class="portfolio-hero">
            <div class="portfolio-contents">
                <h2>Hello, I'm a Student</h2>
                <h1>My name is John Doe</h1>
                <p>I am a passionate web developer. I have experience in building responsive websites and web applications. Apart from that, I enjoy learning new technologies and improving my skills. My hobbies include hiking, photography, and playing the guitar.</p>
                <div class="portfolio-contact">
                    <a href="#contact" class="contact-button">Contact Me</a>
                    <a href="#portfolio" class="edit-button">My  Portfolio</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-image">
                <img src="assets/portfolio-image.jpg" alt="Portfolio Image">
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="portfolio-biography">
            <div class="biography-image">
                <img src="assets/biography-image.jpg" alt="Biography Image">
            </div>
            <div class="biography-content">
                <h3>My Biography</h3>
                <h2>A lead web developer with a passion for creating dynamic and responsive web applications.</h2>
                <p>I am a student with a keen interest in web development. I have worked on several projects that showcase my skills in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. I am always eager to learn new technologies and improve my coding skills. My goal is to become a full-stack developer and contribute to open-source projects.</p>
                <div class="quick-info">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Age</h4>
                        <p>20</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Location</h4>
                        <p>New York, USA</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Email</h4>
                        <p>tempmail@example.com</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Phone</h4>
                        <p>+1 234 567 890</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="follow-me">
                    Follow me on:
                    <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
                        GitHub
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
                        LinkedIn
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
                        Twitter
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
                        Instagram
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
                        Facebook
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-me">
                    <button onclick="window.location.href='contact.html'" class="hire-me">Hire Me</button>
                    <a href="assets/cv.pdf" class="download-cv" download>
                        <button type="button">Download CV</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="about" class="about-section">
            <h1>About Me</h1>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="assets/biography-image.jpg" alt="About Image">
                </div>
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2>Hello! I'm John Doe</h2>
                    <p>
                        I am a passionate web developer and student, always eager to learn and grow. My journey in tech started with curiosity and has grown into a deep love for building beautiful, functional web applications.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I enjoy working with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and modern frameworks. My goal is to become a full-stack developer and contribute to impactful projects. Outside of coding, I love hiking, photography, and music.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="about-list">
                        <li><strong>Age:</strong> 20</li>
                        <li><strong>Location:</strong> New York, USA</li>
                        <li><strong>Email:</strong> tempmail@example.com</li>
                        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 234 567 890</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="services" class="services-section">
            <h1>My Services</h1>
            <div class="services-content">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Web Development</h2>
                    <p>Building responsive and modern websites using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like React.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>UI/UX Design</h2>
                    <p>Designing user-friendly interfaces and experiences for web and mobile applications.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Backend Development</h2>
                    <p>Creating robust server-side logic with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <h2>Project Collaboration</h2>
                    <p>Working with teams using Git, GitHub, and agile methodologies.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="portfolio" class="portfolio-section">
            <h1>My Portfolio</h1>
            <div class="portfolio-content">
                <p>Showcase your projects here...</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="blog" class="blog-section">
            <h1>My Blog</h1>
            <div class="blog-grid">
                <article class="blog-post">
                    <div class="blog-image">
                        <img src="assets/feature1.jpg" alt="Blog Post 1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-content">
                        <h2>Getting Started with Web Development</h2>
                        <p class="blog-date">January 15, 2024</p>
                        <p>Learn the fundamentals of web development and how to build your first website...</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </article>
                
                <article class="blog-post">
                    <div class="blog-image">
                        <img src="assets/feature2.jpg" alt="Blog Post 2">
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-content">
                        <h2>JavaScript Tips and Tricks</h2>
                        <p class="blog-date">February 8, 2024</p>
                        <p>Discover useful JavaScript techniques that will make your code more efficient...</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </article>
                
                <article class="blog-post">
                    <div class="blog-image">
                        <img src="assets/feature3.jpg" alt="Blog Post 3">
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-content">
                        <h2>Building Responsive Websites</h2>
                        <p class="blog-date">March 3, 2024</p>
                        <p>Learn how to create websites that look great on all devices...</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
            <h1>Contact Me</h1>
            <div class="contact-content">
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
                    <p>I'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a project in mind or just want to connect, feel free to reach out.</p>
                    <div class="contact-details">
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <h3>Email</h3>
                            <p>tempmail@example.com</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <h3>Phone</h3>
                            <p>+1 234 567 890</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <h3>Location</h3>
                            <p>New York, USA</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <form action="/portfolio/student/contact" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="subject">Subject</label>
                            <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="message">Message</label>
                            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>